data.description: Gorgeous, Bi-level home located in a quiet cul-de-sac in Oakridge School District. This home features 2 bed and 2 bath on main level with walk in closet in master area and 2 bedrooms with spacious living area in finished basement with separate laundry and mechanical room. This 5 year year old home also includes a 2 stall garage with back deck area that leads you down to the fenced in yard with underground sprinkling. Schedule your showing now before its gone. Welcome home!!
